{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"eunomia-bpf","page":{"layout":"document","title":"build on android aarch64","description":"Android上build需要先Installing Debian on Android in Termux","bodyHtml":"<p>Android上build需要先Installing Debian on Android in Termux</p>\n<p>在Android上构建时，需要先Installing Debian on Android in Termux</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>install termux</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/termux/termux-app/releases/tag/v0.118.0\">https://github.com/termux/termux-app/releases/tag/v0.118.0</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>install proot-distro</p>\n<p>select debian distro</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">pkg</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> proot-distro</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">proot-distro</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> debian</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">proot-distro</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> login</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> debian</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>install packages</p>\n<p>remember <code>proot-distro login debian</code> first</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apk</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> update</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apt</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> clang</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> cmake</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf1</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf-dev</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> zlib1g-dev</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>之后的步骤和在ARM上build上相同</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"build-on-arm\">Build on ARM</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>同步 eunomia-bpf 到本地</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">git</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> clone</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf.git</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">cd</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> eunomia-bpf</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">git</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> submodule</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> update</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --init</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --recursive</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --remote</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>配置环境变量</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">export</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> PKG_CONFIG_PATH</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">/usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu/pkgconfig</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装依赖</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apt</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> update</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apt</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> clang</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> cmake</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf1</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf-dev</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> zlib1g-dev</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改wasm-runtime/CMakeLists.txt<code>中的</code>WAMR_BUILD_TARGET（may not required）</p>\n<p>change <code>set (WAMR_BUILD_TARGET \"X86_64\")</code> to <code>set (WAMR_BUILD_TARGET \"AARCH64\")</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>编译</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> bpf-loader</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>检查输出</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">root@localhost:~/eunomia-bpf#</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> file</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli/build/bin/Release/ecli</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">ecli:</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ELF</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> 64-bit</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> LSB</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> pie</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> executable,</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ARM</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> aarch64,</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> version</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> (SYSV), dynamically linked, interpreter /lib/ld-linux-aarch64.so.1, BuildID[sha1]</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">eab42b79be75951e3a573aa7c61136239d35c868,</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> for</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> GNU/Linux</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> 3.7.0,</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> with</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> debug_info,</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> not</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> stripped</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"id":"build-on-arm","text":"Build on ARM","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2025-02-10T22:38:08.000Z","createdAt":"2025-02-10T22:38:08.000Z","authors":[{"name":"weekendfish","email":"yusen356@gmail.com"}]},"path":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","description":"Simplify eBPF development with CO-RE and WebAssembly. Build, compile, and distribute eBPF programs easier with automatic code generation.","href":"/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"quickstart","description":"- Github Template: eunomia-bpf/eunomia-template - example bpf programs: examples/bpftools - tutorial: eunomia-bpf/bpf-developer-tutorial","href":"/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/"},"next":{"title":"build from source","description":"If you want to run the cli, in most cases, you don't need to build your own.","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"Browse","items":[{"title":"Tutorials","href":"/tutorials/"},{"title":"Blog","href":"/blog/"},{"title":"bpftime","href":"/bpftime/"},{"title":"eBPF×AI/LLMs","href":"/GPTtrace/"},{"title":"eunomia-bpf","href":"/eunomia-bpf/"},{"title":"Ecosystem","href":"/others/"},{"title":"Legacy Blog","href":"/blogs/"}]},{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","href":"/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","depth":1},{"title":"ecli server","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","depth":2},{"title":"exporter","href":"/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","depth":1},{"title":"usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"introduction","href":"/eunomia-bpf/introduction/","depth":1},{"title":"manual","href":"/eunomia-bpf/manual/","depth":1},{"title":"Online Demo","href":"/eunomia-bpf/online/","depth":1},{"title":"quickstart","href":"/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","depth":1},{"title":"build on android aarch64","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","depth":2},{"title":"build from source","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","depth":2},{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/","depth":1},{"title":"supporting-external-BTF","href":"/eunomia-bpf/supporting-external-BTF/","depth":1},{"title":"video","href":"/eunomia-bpf/video/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}